⍝ ZBus.Nats JetStream test suite
⍝ Validates: stream create, JS publish, consumer, JsMsg events, ack
⍝ Requires nats-server -js running on localhost:4222

⎕IO ⎕ML←1
pass←1
tests←0 ⋄ passed←0

dll←'D:\devel\Z-Format\src\ZBus.Nats\bin\Release\net10.0\win-x64\publish\ZBus.Nats.dll'

⍝ ── Define ⎕NA bindings ──────────────────────────────────────────────

'zbus_init'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_init <0T1 >Z'
'zbus_wait'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_wait& <0T1 I4 >Z >Z >Z'
'zbus_close'        ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_close <0T1'
'zbus_describe'     ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_describe <0T1 >Z'
'nats_connect'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_connect <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_stream'       ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_stream <0T1 <0T1 =Z'
'nats_jspub'        ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_jspub <0T1 <0T1 =Z'
'nats_consumer'     ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_consumer <0T1 <0T1 <0T1 =Z'
'nats_ack'          ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_ack <0T1 I8'

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' ZBus.Nats JetStream Tests'
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←''

⍝ ── Setup ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

(rc rootName)←zbus_init 'JS' 0
rc←nats_connect 'JS' 'nats://localhost:4222'
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'JS' 5000 0 0 0
:If evt≢'Connected' ⋄ ⎕←'FATAL: not connected (',evt,')' ⋄ ⎕OFF 1 ⋄ :EndIf
⎕←'Connected to NATS (JetStream enabled)'
⎕←''

⍝ ── Test 1: Create stream ───────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test 1: Create stream'
(rc streamName)←nats_stream 'JS' 'ORDERS' 'orders.>'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ stream created: ',streamName
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ stream creation failed rc=',⍕rc
    ⎕←'  (name=',streamName,')'
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 2: Describe stream ─────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 2: Describe stream'
(rc info)←zbus_describe streamName 0
tests+←1
:If (rc=0)∧((2⊃info)≡'Stream')
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ type=Stream, subjects=',4⊃info
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ describe failed or wrong type, rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 3: JS Publish ──────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 3: JetStream publish'
(rc ack)←nats_jspub 'JS' 'orders.new' 'order-001'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    ⎕←'  stream=',1⊃ack
    ⎕←'  seq=',⍕2⊃ack
    :If (1⊃ack)≡'ORDERS'
        passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ published to ORDERS, seq=',(⍕2⊃ack)
    :Else
        pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ unexpected stream name: ',1⊃ack
    :EndIf
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ jspub failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ Publish a second message
(rc ack2)←nats_jspub 'JS' 'orders.new' 'order-002'

⍝ ── Test 4: Create consumer ─────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 4: Create consumer'
(rc consumerName)←nats_consumer streamName 'proc' '' 'all'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ consumer created: ',consumerName
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ consumer creation failed rc=',(⍕rc),' name=',consumerName
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 5: Receive JsMsg events ────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 5: Receive JsMsg events'

⍝ Should receive the two messages we published
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'JS' 5000 0 0 0
tests+←1
:If evt≡'JsMsg'
    msgSubj←1⊃data
    msgPayload←2⊃data
    msgSeq←4⊃data
    ⎕←'  msg1: subject=',msgSubj,' seq=',⍕msgSeq
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ first JsMsg received'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ expected JsMsg, got ',evt,' on ',obj
:EndIf

(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'JS' 5000 0 0 0
tests+←1
:If evt≡'JsMsg'
    msgSeq2←4⊃data
    ⎕←'  msg2: seq=',⍕msgSeq2
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ second JsMsg received'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ expected second JsMsg, got ',evt
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 6: Acknowledge messages ────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 6: Acknowledge messages'
rc←nats_ack consumerName msgSeq
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ ack seq ',(⍕msgSeq),' rc=0'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ ack failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

rc←nats_ack consumerName msgSeq2
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ ack seq ',(⍕msgSeq2),' rc=0'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ ack failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Cleanup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
rc←zbus_close ⊂'JS'

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' Results: ',(⍕passed),'/',(⍕tests),' passed'
:If pass
    ⎕←' ═══ ALL JETSTREAM TESTS PASSED ═══'
:Else
    ⎕←' *** SOME TESTS FAILED ***'
:EndIf
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
